s nav-menu-links--wide\"><a href=\"#quote-upload\">智能报价</a><a href=\"#quote-upload\">快速原型</a><a href=\"#quote-upload\">DFM可制造性检查</a><a href=\"#quote-upload\">快速报价</a><a href=\"#quote-upload\">图生3D模型</a><a href=\"#quote-upload\">文生3D模型</a><a href=\"#quote-upload\">3D格式转换</a><a href=\"#quote-upload\">3D转2D工程图</a><a href=\"#quote-upload\">2D气泡图标注</a></div><div class=\"nav-menu-preview\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"/precision/solution-cad-cnc-part.png\" alt=\"\"><div class=\"nav-menu-preview-copy\"><strong>需求快速转方案</strong><span>让图纸、模型和文字需求更快进入制造评估。</span></div></div></div></div>\n      <div class=\"nav-dropdown\"><a class=\"nav-item\" href=\"/industries\">行业</a><div class=\"nav-menu\"><div class=\"nav-menu-intro\"><strong>行业</strong><span>面向重点行业场景沉淀制造经验。</span></div><div class=\"nav-menu-links nav-menu-links--wide\"><a href=\"/industries/aerospace\">航天</a><a href=\"/industries/medical\">医疗器械</a><a href=\"/industries/automotive\">汽车</a><a href=\"/industries/robotics\">机器人技术</a><a href=\"/industries/electronics\">电子</a><a href=\"/industries/telecom\">通信</a><a href=\"/industries/semiconductor\">半导体</a><a href=\"/industries/new-energy\">新能源</a><a href=\"/industries/consumer\">消费品</a></div><div class=\"nav-menu-preview\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"/precision/manufacturing-service.png\" alt=\"\"><div class=\"nav-menu-preview-copy\"><strong>行业制造方案</strong><span>匹配行业零件的材料、工艺和质量资料。</span></div></div></div></div>\n      <div class=\"nav-dropdown\"><a class=\"nav-item active\" href=\"/resources\">资源中心</a><div class=\"nav-menu\"><div class=\"nav-menu-intro\"><strong>资源中心</strong><span>制造知识、案例、指南与资料准备。</span></div><div class=\"nav-menu-links nav-menu-links--wide\"><a href=\"/resources/process-guide\">工艺指南</a><a href=\"#\">模型社区</a><a href=\"/resources/material-handbook\">材料手册</a><a href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">设计规范</a><a href=\"/resources/faq\">帮助FAQ</a><a href=\"/resources#downloads\">下载中心</a><a href=\"/resources#news\">新闻动态</a></div><div class=\"nav-menu-preview\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"/precision/insight-guide.jpg\" alt=\"\"><div class=\"nav-menu-preview-copy\"><strong>知识与案例</strong><span>降低前期判断成本，提高项目沟通效率。</span></div></div></div></div>\n      <div class=\"nav-dropdown\"><a class=\"nav-item\" href=\"/about\">关于</a><div class=\"nav-menu\"><div class=\"nav-menu-intro\"><strong>关于</strong><span>团队、质量体系与服务支持。</span></div><div class=\"nav-menu-links nav-menu-links--wide\"><a href=\"/about\">关于我们</a><a href=\"/about/company\">公司介绍</a><a href=\"/about/quality\">质量保证</a><a href=\"/about#service\">服务支持</a><a href=\"/about/privacy\">隐私政策</a><a href=\"/about/terms\">服务条款</a><a href=\"/about#contact\">联系我们</a></div><div class=\"nav-menu-preview\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"/precision/factory-floor.jpg\" alt=\"\"><div class=\"nav-menu-preview-copy\"><strong>可靠制造伙伴</strong><span>以过程透明和质量闭环支持长期合作。</span></div></div></div></div>\n    </nav>\n    <div class=\"nav-actions\"><a class=\"login-link\" href=\"#\">登录</a><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#quote-upload\">立即报价</a><a class=\"lang-link\" href=\"/en/resources\">EN</a></div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<main>\n  <section class=\"template-hero resource-hero\">\n    <div class=\"container template-hero-inner\">\n      <div class=\"template-hero-copy\"><span class=\"template-kicker\">RESOURCE CENTER</span><h1>制造知识、案例与资料</h1><p>精密零部件研发与生产全流程参考阵地。在这里你可以查阅加工工艺详解、材料性能参数、真实落地零部件案例，下载标准化工程资料。从零件设计 DFM 审查、工艺选型、材料比对，到报价沟通、出货验收，一站式获取工业制造参考信息，高效推进零部件项目落地。</p></div>\n      <div class=\"template-hero-panel\"><img src=\"/precision/insight-guide.jpg\" alt=\"制造资源指南\"><div class=\"template-panel-row\"><strong>Guides</strong><span>工艺与材料指南</span></div><div class=\"template-panel-row\"><strong>Cases</strong><span>行业应用案例</span></div></div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"template-section\" id=\"guides\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"template-section-head\"><h2>资源分类</h2><p>覆盖工艺、材料、设计规范、常见问题和下载资料，支撑报价前的制造判断。</p></div>\n      <div class=\"resource-grid\">\n        <article><a href=\"/resources/process-guide\"><img src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\" alt=\"材料指南\"><div><span>GUIDE</span><h3>材料选择指南</h3><p>按强度、重量、耐腐蚀、成本和加工适配性筛选材料。</p></div></a></article>\n        <article><img src=\"/precision/quality-process.jpg\" alt=\"工艺指南\"><div><span>PROCESS</span><h3>工艺与表面处理</h3><p>理解 CNC、3D 打印、钣金和常见后处理的适用边界。</p></div></article>\n        <article id=\"cases\"><img src=\"/precision/case-medical.jpg\" alt=\"行业案例\"><div><span>CASE</span><h3>行业案例</h3><p>沉淀航天、医疗、汽车、电子等场景的典型项目经验。</p></div></article>\n        <article id=\"downloads\"><img src=\"/precision/insight-knowledge.jpg\" alt=\"下载中心\"><div><span>DOWNLOAD</span><h3>下载中心</h3><p>用于报价、DFM、质量文件和项目沟通的资料清单。</p></div></article>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n    <!-- ========== 模型社区 ========== -->\n\n     <section class=\"template-section model-community-section\" id=\"model-community\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"template-section-head model-community-head\">\n        <div>\n          <span class=\"template-kicker\">MODEL COMMUNITY</span>\n          <h2>3D 模型社区</h2>\n          <p>浏览、下载、分享适配 CNC 加工、3D 打印、钣金、注塑、铸造工艺的工业零部件 3D 模型库。平台兼容 STEP、IGES、STL、OBJ 等主流三维格式，可供研发工程师参考成熟零件结构、评估设计可制造性。你也可以上传自有三维模型，和行业从业者交流结构设计思路。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"model-community-actions\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">进入模型中心</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\">上传模型</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- 搜索与筛选栏 -->\n      <div class=\"model-filter-bar\">\n        <div class=\"model-search\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><path d=\"M20 20l-4.3-4.3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg>\n          <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"搜索模型、零件或工艺...\" aria-label=\"搜索模型\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"model-filter-chips\">\n          <button class=\"model-chip active\" data-filter=\"all\">全部</button>\n          <button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"cnc\">CNC加工</button>\n          <button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"3dprint\">3D打印</button>\n          <button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"sheet\">钣金</button>\n          <button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"injection\">注塑</button>\n          <button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"casting\">铸造</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- 模型网格 -->\n      <div class=\"model-grid\">\n        <article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"cnc\">\n          <div class=\"model-card-media\">\n            <img src=\"/precision/service-cnc.jpg\" alt=\"精密轴类零件\">\n            <div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n              <span class=\"model-format\">STEP</span>\n              <button class=\"model-fav\" aria-label=\"收藏\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"model-card-body\">\n            <h3>精密轴类零件</h3>\n            <p>适用于数控车削加工，含完整公差标注</p>\n            <div class=\"model-meta\">\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">CNC</span>\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">不锈钢</span>\n              <span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 1.2k</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"3dprint\">\n          <div class=\"model-card-media\">\n            <img src=\"/precision/product-flange.jpg\" alt=\"法兰连接件\">\n            <div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n              <span class=\"model-format\">STL</span>\n              <button class=\"model-fav\" aria-label=\"收藏\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"model-card-body\">\n            <h3>法兰连接件</h3>\n            <p>金属3D打印优化结构，轻量化设计</p>\n            <div class=\"model-meta\">\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">3D打印</span>\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">钛合金</span>\n              <span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 856</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"sheet\">\n          <div class=\"model-card-media\">\n            <img src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\" alt=\"钣金支架\">\n            <div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n              <span class=\"model-format\">DXF</span>\n              <button class=\"model-fav\" aria-label=\"收藏\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"model-card-body\">\n            <h3>钣金支架</h3>\n            <p>激光切割折弯工艺，含展开图</p>\n            <div class=\"model-meta\">\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">钣金</span>\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">铝合金</span>\n              <span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 2.1k</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"injection\">\n          <div class=\"model-card-media\">\n            <img src=\"/precision/quality-process.jpg\" alt=\"注塑外壳\">\n            <div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n              <span class=\"model-format\">IGES</span>\n              <button class=\"model-fav\" aria-label=\"收藏\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"model-card-body\">\n            <h3>注塑外壳</h3>\n            <p>ABS材质，含拔模斜度和分型线</p>\n            <div class=\"model-meta\">\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">注塑</span>\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">ABS</span>\n              <span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 643</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"cnc\">\n          <div class=\"model-card-media\">\n            <img src=\"/precision/product-shaft.jpg\" alt=\"传动轴\">\n            <div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n              <span class=\"model-format\">STEP</span>\n              <button class=\"model-fav\" aria-label=\"收藏\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"model-card-body\">\n            <h3>传动轴</h3>\n            <p>多台阶轴类，含键槽和螺纹特征</p>\n            <div class=\"model-meta\">\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">CNC</span>\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">碳钢</span>\n              <span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 987</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"3dprint\">\n          <div class=\"model-card-media\">\n            <img src=\"/precision/case-medical.jpg\" alt=\"医疗器械支架\">\n            <div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n              <span class=\"model-format\">STL</span>\n              <button class=\"model-fav\" aria-label=\"收藏\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"model-card-body\">\n            <h3>医疗器械支架</h3>\n            <p>微纳3D打印，生物相容性材料</p>\n            <div class=\"model-meta\">\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">3D打印</span>\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">树脂</span>\n              <span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 432</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"casting\">\n          <div class=\"model-card-media\">\n            <img src=\"/precision/service-finishing.jpg\" alt=\"阀体铸件\">\n            <div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n              <span class=\"model-format\">STEP</span>\n              <button class=\"model-fav\" aria-label=\"收藏\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"model-card-body\">\n            <h3>阀体铸件</h3>\n            <p>砂型铸造工艺，含浇冒口设计</p>\n            <div class=\"model-meta\">\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">铸造</span>\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">铜合金</span>\n              <span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 321</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"cnc\">\n          <div class=\"model-card-media\">\n            <img src=\"/precision/factory-floor.jpg\" alt=\"复杂腔体零件\">\n            <div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n              <span class=\"model-format\">IGES</span>\n              <button class=\"model-fav\" aria-label=\"收藏\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"model-card-body\">\n            <h3>复杂腔体零件</h3>\n            <p>五轴联动加工，含曲面特征</p>\n            <div class=\"model-meta\">\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">CNC</span>\n              <span class=\"model-tag\">铝合金</span>\n              <span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 756</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- 社区统计 -->\n      <div class=\"model-community-stats\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>12,580+</strong>\n          <span>模型资源</span>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <strong>8,200+</strong>\n          <span>活跃用户</span>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <strong>45,000+</strong>\n          <span>月下载量</span>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <strong>6</strong>\n          <span>支持格式</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n\n\n  <section class=\"template-section resource-library\">\n    <div class=\"container library-layout\">\n      <article class=\"library-feature\">\n        <span class=\"template-kicker\">RESOURCE MAP</span>\n        <h2>资源中心</h2>\n        <p>一站式获取精密零部件项目所需全部参考资源</p>\n        <!-- <a href=\"/resources/process-guide\">查看工艺指南</a> -->\n      </article>\n      <div class=\"library-list\">\n        <a href=\"/resources/process-guide\"><b>01</b><strong>工艺指南</strong><span>CNC 加工、3D 打印、钣金、注塑、铸造、表面处理全品类工艺参数、选型优劣对比，为零件方案设计提供依据。</span></a>\n        <a href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\"><b>02</b><strong>设计规范</strong><span>提供精密零部件 DFM 设计准则、加工结构规范、公差与工程图纸标准，助力优化零件设计，提升可制造性。</span></a>\n        <a href=\"#downloads\"><b>03</b><strong>资料下载</strong><span>DFM 可制造性检查清单、工程图纸规范、验收标准、报价配套模板等工程文件，支持直接下载使用。</span></a>\n        <a href=\"#news\"><b>04</b><strong>新闻动态</strong><span>制造技术科普、行业前沿资讯、平台内容更新通知、零部件项目技术复盘分享。</span></a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n    <!-- ========== 工艺指南 ========== -->\n  <section class=\"template-section process-guide-section\" id=\"process-guide\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"template-section-head\">\n        <span class=\"template-kicker\">PROCESS GUIDE</span>\n        <h2>工艺指南</h2>\n        <p>汇集主流精密制造工艺知识库，面向研发、采购工程师提供选型参考。你可以快速了解每种加工方式适用零件形态、材料范围、精度上限、表面处理能力，在项目前期完成工艺对比，规避设计无法加工、成本超标、交付周期失控等问题。</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"process-guide-layout\">\n        <!-- 左侧导航 -->\n        <aside class=\"process-guide-nav\">\n          <h3>工艺目录</h3>\n          <nav>\n            <a href=\"#cnc-guide\" class=\"active\"><b>01</b><span>数控加工</span></a>\n            <a href=\"#3dprint-guide\"><b>02</b><span>3D 打印</span></a>\n            <a href=\"#sheet-guide\"><b>03</b><span>钣金加工</span></a>\n            <a href=\"#injection-guide\"><b>04</b><span>注塑成型</span></a>\n            <a href=\"#casting-guide\"><b>05</b><span>铸造工艺</span></a>\n            <a href=\"#surface-guide\"><b>06</b><span>表面处理</span></a>\n          </nav>\n        </aside>\n\n        <!-- 右侧内容 -->\n        <div class=\"process-guide-content\">\n          <!-- 数控加工 -->\n          <article class=\"process-guide-panel is-active\" id=\"cnc-guide\">\n            <div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n              <img src=\"/precision/service-cnc.jpg\" alt=\"数控加工\">\n              <div>\n                <span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 01</span>\n                <h3>数控加工（CNC）</h3>\n                <p>CNC 数控加工依靠数控程序驱动刀具完成材料去除加工，能够实现复杂型腔、异形曲面、高精度孔系结构成型，既支持单件样品试制、中小批量试产，也可承接稳定规模化量产，广泛应用于金属与高性能工程塑料精密零部件制造</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n              <div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n                  <b>适用材料</b>\n                  <p>铝合金、不锈钢、碳钢、铜合金、钛合金；POM、PEEK、尼龙、PC、亚克力等工程塑料。可依据零件载荷、使用环境、轻量化需求完成材质比对选型。</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n                  <b>精度范围</b>\n                  <p>常规量产加工精度 ±0.05mm；精密加工等级可达 ±0.01mm；超高精密定制加工最高可达 ±0.005mm。零件壁厚、结构形态、装夹方案都会影响最终可实现精度。</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n                  <b>表面粗糙度</b>\n                  <p>标准铣削表面 Ra 0.8–3.2μm；精加工可达到 Ra 0.4μm；搭配抛光工序可实现 Ra 0.2μm 镜面效果。粗糙度直接影响零件装配密封性、摩擦特性以及阳极氧化、电镀等后续表面处理效果。</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n                  <b>典型交期</b>\n                  <p>常规结构零件 3–7 天；多工序复杂异形零件 7–14 天；型腔模具、超高精密定制零部件 14–30 天，可根据订单排产协调交付计划。</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n                <h4>加工流程</h4>\n                <ol>\n                  <li><div><strong>图纸审核</strong><span>梳理图纸尺寸基准、公差要求、装配工况，提前识别结构加工难点与设计风险。</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>工艺规划</strong><span>规划完整加工工序，选定适配刀具与工装方案，平衡零件加工成本、加工效率与成品质量。</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>编程仿真</strong><span>CAM 程序编写与路径仿真模拟，规避加工过切、撞刀风险，保障加工安全性。</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>首件试切</strong><span>试制首件完成全尺寸检测，确认尺寸精度、外观质量达标，固化稳定加工工艺。</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>批量生产</strong><span>量产阶段持续抽样检测，依托标准化过程管控，保障大批量零件尺寸一致性。</span></div></li>\n                </ol>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"/capabilities/process/cnc\" class=\"text-link\">查看完整 CNC 指南 →</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <!-- 3D 打印 -->\n          <article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"3dprint-guide\">\n            <div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n              <img src=\"/precision/product-flange.jpg\" alt=\"3D打印\">\n              <div>\n                <span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 02</span>\n                <h3>3D 打印</h3>\n                <p>增材制造技术，通过逐层堆积材料成型复杂几何结构，适合快速原型和小批量定制。</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n              <div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n                  <b>工艺类型</b>\n                  <p>SLA（光固化）、SLS（选择性激光烧结）、FDM（熔融沉积）、SLM（金属激光熔化）</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n                  <b>精度范围</b>\n                  <p>SLA ±0.1mm，SLS ±0.2mm，FDM ±0.3mm，SLM ±0.05mm</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n                  <b>层厚选择</b>\n                  <p>0.025mm（微纳级），0.05-0.1mm（精密级），0.2-0.3mm（标准级）</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n                  <b>典型交期</b>\n                  <p>1-3 天（快速原型），3-7 天（功能件），7-14 天（金属件）</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n                <h4>打印流程</h4>\n                <ol>\n                  <li><div><strong>模型准备</strong><span>STL 文件修复、壁厚检查和支撑添加</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>切片处理</strong><span>层厚、填充率和打印方向优化</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>打印监控</strong><span>实时温度、层间附着和变形控制</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>后处理</strong><span>去除支撑、表面打磨和热处理</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>质量检测</strong><span>尺寸扫描、密度测试和力学性能验证</span></div></li>\n                </ol>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"/capabilities/process/micro-3d\" class=\"text-link\">查看完整 3D 打印指南 →</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <!-- 其他工艺面板（钣金、注塑、铸造、表面处理）保持相同结构，简略展示 -->\n          <article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"sheet-guide\">\n            <div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n              <img src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\" alt=\"钣金加工\">\n              <div>\n                <span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 03</span>\n                <h3>钣金加工</h3>\n                <p>激光切割、数控折弯和冲压成型，适用于薄板金属件的高效生产。</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n              <div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>适用材料</b><p>冷轧钢板、不锈钢板、铝板、铜板，厚度 0.5-6mm</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>精度范围</b><p>切割 ±0.1mm，折弯 ±0.2mm，孔位 ±0.05mm</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>表面处理</b><p>喷涂、电镀、阳极氧化、拉丝、钝化</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>典型交期</b><p>2-5 天（简单件），5-10 天（复杂焊接件）</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n                <h4>加工流程</h4>\n                <ol>\n                  <li><div><strong>图纸审核</strong><span>确认展开尺寸、折弯顺序和公差要求</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>激光切割</strong><span>高精度切割下料，保证尺寸准确性</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>数控折弯</strong><span>按顺序折弯成型，控制回弹</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>焊接组装</strong><span>必要时进行点焊或弧焊</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>表面处理</strong><span>打磨、喷涂或电镀</span></div></li>\n                </ol>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"/capabilities/process/sheet-metal\" class=\"text-link\">查看完整钣金指南 →</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"injection-guide\">\n            <div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n              <img src=\"/precision/quality-process.jpg\" alt=\"注塑成型\">\n              <div>\n                <span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 04</span>\n                <h3>注塑成型</h3>\n                <p>热塑性塑料熔融高压注入模具型腔，适合大批量塑料零件生产。</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n              <div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>适用材料</b><p>ABS、PP、PC、PA、POM、PEEK、TPE 等</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>精度范围</b><p>一般级 ±0.1mm，精密级 ±0.05mm，超精密级 ±0.02mm</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>模具寿命</b><p>10 万次（铝模），30-50 万次（钢模），100 万次（硬模）</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>典型交期</b><p>7-14 天（手板），20-35 天（软模），35-60 天（硬模）</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n                <h4>成型流程</h4>\n                <ol>\n                  <li><div><strong>模具设计</strong><span>确定分型面、浇口位置和冷却系统</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>模具制造</strong><span>CNC加工、电火花和抛光</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>试模调整</strong><span>优化工艺参数，验证尺寸和外观</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>批量生产</strong><span>稳定工艺，控制周期和质量</span></div></li>\n                </ol>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"/capabilities/process/injection\" class=\"text-link\">查看完整注塑指南 →</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"casting-guide\">\n            <div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n              <img src=\"/precision/service-finishing.jpg\" alt=\"铸造工艺\">\n              <div>\n                <span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 05</span>\n                <h3>铸造工艺</h3>\n                <p>将熔融金属浇入铸型获得毛坯，适用于复杂形状和大型金属件。</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n              <div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>工艺类型</b><p>砂型铸造、熔模铸造、压铸、离心铸造、连续铸造</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>适用材料</b><p>铸铁、铸钢、铝合金、铜合金、锌合金、镁合金</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>精度范围</b><p>CT7-CT9（砂铸），CT4-CT6（熔模），CT3-CT5（压铸）</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>典型交期</b><p>15-30 天（砂铸），20-45 天（熔模），10-20 天（压铸）</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n                <h4>铸造流程</h4>\n                <ol>\n                  <li><div><strong>模具制作</strong><span>木模、金属模或蜡模制作</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>砂型/壳型</strong><span>造型、制芯和烘干</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>熔炼浇注</strong><span>金属熔化、精炼和浇铸</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>清理检验</strong><span>去除浇冒口、喷砂和无损检测</span></li>\n                </ol>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"/capabilities/process/polyurethane\" class=\"text-link\">查看完整铸造指南 →</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"surface-guide\">\n            <div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n              <img src=\"/precision/product-shaft.jpg\" alt=\"表面处理\">\n              <div>\n                <span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 06</span>\n                <h3>表面处理</h3>\n                <p>改善零件外观、耐腐蚀性和功能特性的后处理工艺。</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n              <div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>适用材料</b><p>铝合金、不锈钢、碳钢、铜合金、钛合金、工程塑料</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>工艺类型</b><p>阳极氧化、电镀、喷涂、粉末喷涂、热处理、激光打标、抛光、钝化</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>膜厚范围</b><p>阳极氧化 5-25μm，电镀 3-50μm，喷涂 40-120μm</p></div>\n                <div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>典型交期</b><p>2-5 天（标准件），5-10 天（复杂件），7-14 天（特殊工艺）</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n                <h4>处理流程</h4>\n                <ol>\n                  <li><div><strong>表面预处理</strong><span>脱脂、酸洗、研磨去除氧化层和杂质</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>工艺实施</strong><span>按选定工艺进行表面处理</span></div></li>\n                  <li><div><strong>质量检测</strong><span>膜厚、硬度、附着力和耐腐蚀性测试</span></div></li>\n                </ol>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"/capabilities/finish\" class=\"text-link\">查看完整表面处理指南 →</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n\n  <section class=\"template-section soft\" id=\"news\">\n    <div class=\"container resource-feature\">\n      <div class=\"template-section-head\"><h2>推荐阅读</h2><p>精选与工艺选择、材料判断和质量验收相关的文章，帮助客户补齐项目前期信息。</p></div>\n      <div class=\"article-list\">\n        <a href=\"#\"><strong>CNC 精密加工前需要确认哪些图纸信息？</strong><span>工艺指南 / 6 min read</span></a>\n        <a href=\"#\"><strong>铝合金、钛合金和不锈钢在轻量化结构中的取舍</strong><span>材料指南 / 8 min read</span></a>\n        <a href=\"#\"><strong>首件检测、CMM 与交付资料如何配合项目验收？</strong><span>质量资料 / 5 min read</span></a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"template-section\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"template-section-head\"><h2>资源使用路径</h2><p>按选材料、定工艺、看案例和备资料的顺序，帮助客户逐步完成项目准备。</p></div>\n      <div class=\"resource-path\">\n        <div><strong>选材料</strong><span>根据零件功能、成本、环境和加工方式筛选候选材料。</span></div>\n        <div><strong>定工艺</strong><span>理解 CNC、3D 打印、钣金、表面处理的适用边界。</span></div>\n        <div><strong>看案例</strong><span>参考类似行业和零件类型的制造方案与交付资料。</span></div>\n        <div><strong>备资料</strong><span>准备图纸、模型、数量、质量要求和报价输入信息。</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</main>\n\n<footer class=\"footer\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"footer-grid footer-grid--expanded\"><div class=\"footer-brand\"><a class=\"brand\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"敏捷智造首页\"><svg class=\"brand-symbol\" viewbox=\"0 0 56 58\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><path class=\"brand-symbol-secondary\" d=\"M28 3 4 17l9.8 5.7L28 14.5l14.2 8.2L52 17 28 3Z\"></path><path class=\"brand-symbol-primary\" d=\"M2 20.8 28 36l26-15.2v29.4l-9.8 5.7V37.7L28 47 11.8 37.7v18.2L2 50.2V20.8Z\"></path><path class=\"brand-symbol-secondary\" d=\"M17 42.7 28 49l11-6.3v8.8L28 58l-11-6.5v-8.8Z\"></path></svg><span class=\"brand-wordmark\"><strong>敏捷智造</strong><span>AGILE MANUFACTURING</span></span></a><p>为客户提供高品质、高稳定性的精密制造服务。</p><div class=\"footer-socials\" aria-label=\"Share and contact apps\">\n  <a class=\"footer-social-link\" href=\"weixin://\" aria-label=\"WeChat\" title=